  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a ring of insects that spin around you violently. Creatures of your choice in a 5-foot radius sphere centered on you must succeed a dexterity saving throw, taking 3d8 poison damage on a failed save or half as much on a success as they start their turns in the target radius or attempt to enter the target radius.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, the radius by 5 feet and the damage by 2d8.</p>",
